Resource Profile: ASOrganization

Official URL: http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/as03/StructureDefinition/AS-Organization Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2023-03-16 Computable Name: ASOrganization

Profil créé à partir de la ressource FrOrganization dans le cadre de l’annuaire santé - décrit les organismes du domaine sanitaire, médico-social et social.

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide

Constraints

IdGradePath(s)DetailsRequirements
cpt-2errorOrganization.telecom, Organization.contact.telecomA system is required if a value is provided.
: value.empty() or system.exists()
ele-1error**ALL** elementsAll FHIR elements must have a @value or children
: hasValue() or (children().count() > id.count())
ext-1error**ALL** extensionsMust have either extensions or value[x], not both
: extension.exists() != value.exists()
org-2errorOrganization.addressAn address of an organization can never be of use 'home'
: where(use = 'home').empty()
org-3errorOrganization.telecomThe telecom of an organization can never be of use 'home'
: where(use = 'home').empty()
per-1errorOrganization.telecom.periodIf present, start SHALL have a lower value than end
: start.hasValue().not() or end.hasValue().not() or (start <= end)
ref-1errorOrganization.partOfSHALL have a contained resource if a local reference is provided
: reference.startsWith('#').not() or (reference.substring(1).trace('url') in %rootResource.contained.id.trace('ids'))
